# Private SEO / analytics / API data
# ============================================================

data/
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.db
*.duckdb
*.parquet
*.arrow
*.feather
*.csv
*.tsv

# Keep public prompt CSVs possible later only if explicitly unignored.
!prompts/**/*.csv

