*.temp
~$*

# ============================================================
# Public allow-list notes
# ============================================================

# Allowed for GitHub:
# - README.md
# - apps/ and tools/ source code with no secrets
# - prompts/ generic work prompts with no real metrics or client data
# - docs/ public repository policy documents
# - db/migrations/ schema files once created
